00:03:05,560 --> 00:03:08,500
Didn’t we promise that we won’t
send gifts to each other on our birthday?



00:03:09,080 --> 00:03:10,180
This year is special.



00:03:11,020 --> 00:03:12,180
I want to send a gift to you.



00:03:15,160 --> 00:03:15,800
Do you like it?



00:03:20,500 --> 00:03:22,100
I’m afraid I don’t any chance to do it again.



00:03:23,200 --> 00:03:24,100
It’s lovely.



00:03:25,200 --> 00:03:26,600
I think



00:03:26,940 --> 00:03:30,320
it resembles you somehow.



00:03:30,700 --> 00:03:31,500
It’s so cute.



00:03:34,820 --> 00:03:35,579
Jin Mi.



00:03:36,800 --> 00:03:38,180
You’re kind to me.



00:03:41,900 --> 00:03:44,200
It’s a pity that I can’t marry anyone,



00:03:44,680 --> 00:03:45,720
so I can



00:03:46,040 --> 00:03:47,579
only love you.



00:03:49,340 --> 00:03:50,900
Come on. Let’s go on drinking.



00:03:51,140 --> 00:03:52,060
Cheers.



00:04:09,660 --> 00:04:11,520
Why is this place so familiar?



00:04:12,720 --> 00:04:14,180
I seem to have been here before.



00:04:27,440 --> 00:04:28,200
Frost flower.



00:04:29,960 --> 00:04:31,780
