All mothers in the world



00:13:34,440 --> 00:13:36,340
hope their children are happy.



00:13:36,860 --> 00:13:39,340
Lord Dongting knows



00:13:40,440 --> 00:13:41,820
your life of the day most clearly.



00:13:42,560 --> 00:13:46,460
I think she can understand your choice.



00:14:04,240 --> 00:14:05,080
Foster mother is stubborn.



00:14:05,580 --> 00:14:06,580
Please forgive her.



00:14:11,180 --> 00:14:11,860
That’s okay.



00:14:13,840 --> 00:14:14,640
I can



00:14:15,240 --> 00:14:16,420
speak to her here.



00:14:30,680 --> 00:14:32,880
I was mean to you yesterday.



00:14:34,100 --> 00:14:35,680
I’m so sorry, mom.



00:14:37,340 --> 00:14:40,580
After I left, I recalled some past events



00:14:41,420 --> 00:14:42,300
and knew that



00:14:43,700 --> 00:14:45,200
I blamed you wrongly.



00:14:47,440 --> 00:14:51,540
It turns out that you didn’t abandon me.



00:14:52,160 --> 00:14:53,640
