00:15:04,160 --> 00:15:06,900
Now we finally meet again after a long separation.



00:15:08,120 --> 00:15:09,400
Seeing that you’re healthy



00:15:09,820 --> 00:15:12,020
and have



00:15:12,020 --> 00:15:13,220
two excellent adopted sons



00:15:13,800 --> 00:15:14,780
to serve you for me,



00:15:17,040 --> 00:15:18,760
I’m so happy



00:15:19,860 --> 00:15:20,880
yet guilty.



00:15:24,800 --> 00:15:27,060
I’m not asking you to forgive me.



00:15:28,240 --> 00:15:29,540
