I wasn’t mad at you.



00:16:45,020 --> 00:16:48,440
I’ve long been indifferent to personal life and death.



00:16:48,640 --> 00:16:53,160
The reason why I’m still alive is that



00:16:53,160 --> 00:16:55,160
I want to avenge the death of my family members.



00:16:56,460 --> 00:16:58,680
Please forgive my cruelty.



00:16:59,600 --> 00:17:02,340
You suffered a lot in your childhood



00:17:02,840 --> 00:17:05,140
because of me.



00:17:05,140 --> 00:17:08,579
Since you have the chance to live freely,



00:17:09,660 --> 00:17:13,660
how I can drag you down to the hell?



00:17:14,280 --> 00:17:16,460
I wish you peace



00:17:18,859 --> 00:17:20,900
and happiness.



00:17:26,099 --> 00:17:27,859
I didn’t see my mom today,



00:17:28,440 --> 00:17:31,640
but I have two brothers instead.



00:17:31,920 --> 00:17:33,160
What a surprise!



00:17:33,980 --> 00:17:34,780
There is still a long time ahead.



00:17:35,680 --> 00:17:37,960
Faith can move mountains.



00:17:39,120 --> 00:17:39,960
I hope



00:17:40,260 --> 00:17:41,960
you can pay more attention to mom.



00:17:42,480 --> 00:17:43,320
Rest assured, Your Highness.



00:17:43,940 --> 00:17:45,380
